# 디자인 시스템

상세: `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` · CSS 변수: `app/globals.css`

## 색상 (@theme / CSS 변수)
- Primary Blue `#5FA8D3` — CTA, 링크
- Dark Navy `#2B3A4A` — 제목, Footer, Booking 배경
- Accent Green `#6B9080` — 전문가 모집
- Accent Green Dark `#5a7e6f` — Recruitment hover
- Neutral: lightBg `#F8F9FA`, borderLight `#E9ECEF`, textGray `#6C757D`

## 타이포
- Noto Sans KR (`app/layout.tsx`)
- `text-wrap: pretty` 권장

## 버튼 (현재 구현)
```tsx
// Primary CTA
"bg-primary-blue ... hover:bg-primary-navy hover:-translate-y-0.5"
// Recruitment submit
"bg-accent-green ... hover:bg-accent-green-dark"
// Kakao
"bg-[#FEE500] text-[#3C1E1E]"
```

## 폼
- 스타일: `components/ui/formStyles.ts` (`inputClassName`, `selectClassName`, `textareaClassName`)
- input: `border-2 border-border-light rounded-lg px-4 py-3`
- focus: `focus:border-primary-blue`

## 카드·모달
- Program Card: `rounded-xl shadow hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-primary-blue`
- Recruitment Modal: `max-w-[874px] w-[95%] max-h-[90vh] rounded-2xl`
- Confirm Modal: `max-w-[500px]`
- Overlay: `fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 z-[2000]`

## 섹션 배경 (구현 기준)
- Hero: `bg-linear-to-br from-[#F0F7FA] to-[#E8F4F8]`
- Booking: `bg-linear-to-br from-primary-navy to-[#1A2832]`
- Recruitment Banner: `bg-linear-to-br from-accent-green to-accent-green-dark`

## 레이아웃
- Container: `max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6` (대부분 섹션)
- Booking inner: `max-w-[1000px]`
- Grid: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6`
- 터치 영역 최소 44px (`min-h-[44px]`)

## 애니메이션
- `animate-slide-down` — 상담 폼 펼침 (`app/globals.css`)
